title: Record-setting day of postseason homers
text:
> Sports Record-setting day of postseason homers New York Mets center fielder Yoenis Cespedes (52) follows through on an three run home run during the fourth inning in Game 3 of baseball’s National League Division Series against the Los Angeles Dodgers, Monday, Oct. 12, 2015, at CitiField in New York. (AP Photo/Frank Franklin II)
